column5: Wow, Christine Cope has got nothing on your wife.  Some beauty esox there! lol
Definitely some nice fish in there!
Awesome dude!!!!!  Is that the lund predator refurbished??
Good for her, that's awesome!!!
Wicked AaaaWESOME!  Great bunch of toothies and grins.
Great bunch of fish! That last one looks heavy. My wife has the golden horseshoe too lol  Pete
Why do women always have to embarrass us on the water? My girlfriend smokes me every time.
That's awesome fellas,as much as I dispise all the bragging and told ya so afterwords lol, the excitement is something I or she won't soon forget
Nice congrats to her and your self for putting her on so many fish.
You know what your doing when your wife can catch the big ones too.

Well my wife's a great fisher woman,this yr she decides she wants to see first hand what all my Muskie fuss is about ...she done well thought I'd share her first season ,,by the way 5 for her 1 for me ?.... . uthb
I guess you can call it beginner's luck. I wish some days I had that luck. Nice fish.
Wowza those are some sweet fish! Awesome colours too, congrats
Great fish.  Are those lauzon skis?
Wow, Christine Cope has got nothing on your wife.  Some beauty esox there!
Very nice indeed, I'd say your wife is having an outstanding year so far.
Awesome pix!  Thanx.  You admitted she out fished you??  Oh well, I guess someone has to put fish in the boat.  LOL!
Lol thanks fellas she did awesome on the walleye hunt too

Nice fish.  That happened to me when I first started fishing - could catch anything.  Then I thought I knew something, and it all went away (sorta like my Golf game too...lol).  Glad you can fish with your wife -   .  Always nice when that can be done together.
Cool! My GF Kills me in the musky game too. Its all good. I'd rather it was her than one of my buddies any day!  S.
That's amazing!
Just awesome! Thanks for sharing.
awesome
nice average size there. You make a good guide
THATS a nice pike too!!!
Thats awesome congrats on a killer time on the water love the colours on that pike
Beauty fish,thanks for posting.
Nice fish great to have a wife who likes to fish
Prob is I'm s walleye boy at heart,,she thinks the only thing that swims now are musky lol
